text: niccayamaka nam israyilin cantatiyanarai, takunta iruppitattil irutti, nalla unavukalaiyum kotuttu vantom; eninum unmaiyana nanam avarkalitam varum varaiyil avarkal marupatu ceyyavillai niccayamaka um iraivan avarkal eta parri marupatu ceytu kontiruntarkalo a(tu visayat)til iruti nalil avarkalitaiye tirppalippan
